{
  "title": "Built-in AI packages\uf0c1",
  "sections": [
    {
      "header": "Starting an AI package\uf0c1",
      "content": [
        {
          "paragraph": "There are two ways to start AI package:"
        },
        {
          "code": "-- from local script add package to selflocalAI=require('openmw.interfaces').AIAI.startPackage(options)-- via event to any actoractor:sendEvent('StartAIPackage',options)"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "optionsis Lua table with arguments of the AI package."
        },
        {
          "code": "options"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "Common arguments that can be used with any AI package"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "name"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "type"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "description"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "type"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "string [required]"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "the name of the package (see packages listed below)"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "cancelOther"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "boolean [default=true]"
        },
        {
          "paragraph": "whether to cancel all other AI packages"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "header": "Combat\uf0c1",
